<title>bʿd mạ knt ʿbd</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bʿd mạ knt ʿbd ạ̉syr wkạnt kẖṭạyạyạ ktyr
 jh yswʿ sẖạlhạ ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb kẖlạny ạ̉myr
 wfy̱ dywny yswʿ
 bʿd ạlḥzn bqyt frḥạn wạtmtʿt bạlgẖfrạn
 wfy ạlsmạ bqy̱ ly mkạn wʿạysẖ fy ạ̉mạn</lyrics>
